This paper is likely to belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category as it deals with the task of extracting keyphrases from news content. It also involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques such as tagging, ranking, and finding roles for keyphrases, which are commonly used in the Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of machine learning techniques to identify the most interesting and informative keyphrases, which falls under the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Deep Learning (cs.DL).
